item.title: late late
item.description: so I am staying late at work tonight to get some stuff.. and I broke my ipod. it just own’t let me put any music on it. so while I was “fixing” it.. I inadvertently removed all my other music. so now there is nothing. doh. i have to get up Soooooooo early tomorrow. like 4:30. suxor.
